OL,3,CUK economy contracts for first time
OL,4,Csince last August
OL,6,FBritain's economy contracted last
OL,7,Fmonth for the first time in eight
OL,8,Fmonths, amid signs that the Iran war
OL,9,Fis beginning to take its toll on some
OL,10,Fsectors.
OL,12,FThe Office for National Statistics
OL,13,F(ONS) said gross domestic product
OL,14,F(GDP) declined by 0.1% in April in a
OL,15,Fsharp pull back from growth of 0.3% in
OL,16,FMarch and 0.4% in February.
OL,18,FThe decline was driven by a 0.2% fall
OL,19,Fin services, which was partially
OL,20,Foffset by a 0.1% rise in construction
OL,21,Fand 0.4% growth in manufacturing.
