OL,3,CUK economy contracts for first time
OL,4,Csince last August
OL,6,FIn the three months to April, GDP grew
OL,7,Fby 0.7%, according to the ONS.
OL,9,FLiz McKeown, ONS director of economic
OL,10,Fstatistics said: "The economy grew in
OL,11,Fthe latest three months as a whole,
OL,12,Freflecting strong growth in February
OL,13,Fand March.
OL,15,F"This was despite April showing a
OL,16,Fsmall fall."
